<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Scene Detail – <%= scene.title %> – LumenNyx Studios</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="model-portal">
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="site-header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand-link">
        <span class="brand-mark">
          <img src="/img/lumennyx-mark.png" alt="LumenNyx Studios logo">
        </span>
        <span class="brand-text">LUMENNYX STUDIOS</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="main-nav">
        <a href="/studio-panel">Studio Panel</a>
        <a href="/studio-panel/models">Models</a>
        <a href="/studio-panel/scenes" class="active">Scenes</a>
        <a href="/2257">2257</a>
        <form action="/logout" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn secondary" style="padding:0.3rem 0.9rem;font-size:0.75rem;">
            Logout
          </button>
        </form>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="page-wrapper">
    <section class="portal-section">
      <h3>Scene Detail – <%= scene.title %></h3>
      <p class="portal-note">
        Internal record for this scene. Tag all performers who appear in this shoot.
        Use the storage note and code fields to find the footage later.
      </p>

      <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="alert error"><%= error %></div>
      <% } %>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Internal code:</strong> <%= scene.code || '-' %></li>
        <li><strong>Shoot date:</strong> <%= scene.shoot_date || '-' %></li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> <%= scene.status || '-' %></li>
        <li><strong>Storage location:</strong> <%= scene.storage_note || '-' %></li>
      </ul>

      <% if (scene.description) { %>
        <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;"><strong>Notes:</strong> <%= scene.description %></p>
      <% } %>
    </section>

    <!-- Tag models into this scene -->
    <section class="portal-section">
      <h3>Tag a Model in This Scene</h3>
      <form action="/studio-panel/scenes/<%= scene.id %>/tag" method="POST" class="portal-form">
        <label>
          Model username (portal login name, case-insensitive)
          <input type="text" name="username" required>
        </label>

        <label>
          Role label (optional – e.g. main, partner, BG, extra)
          <input type="text" name="role_label">
        </label>

        <button type="submit" class="btn primary">Tag Model</button>
      </form>

      <p class="field-help" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
        Only models with portal accounts (role = "model") can be tagged here. This
        helps keep a clean record of which performers appeared in which scenes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Tagged models list -->
    <section class="portal-section">
      <h3>Performers Tagged in This Scene</h3>

      <% if (!tags || tags.length === 0) { %>
        <p>No models have been tagged in this scene yet.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <div class="documents-list">
          <table>
            <thead>
              <tr>
                <th>Username</th>
                <th>Legal Name</th>
                <th>Role</th>
                <th>Model Profile</th>
                <th>Remove</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <% tags.forEach(function(t) { %>
                <tr>
                  <td><%= t.username %></td>
                  <td><%= t.legal_name || '-' %></td>
                  <td><%= t.role_label || '-' %></td>
                  <td>
                    <a href="/studio-panel/models/<%= t.user_id %>" class="btn secondary" style="font-size:0.8rem;padding:0.2rem 0.7rem;">
                      View Model
                    </a>
                  </td>
                  <td>
                    <form action="/studio-panel/scenes/<%= scene.id %>/remove-tag" method="POST" style="display:inline;">
                      <input type="hidden" name="tag_id" value="<%= t.tag_id %>">
                      <button type="submit" class="btn secondary" style="font-size:0.75rem;padding:0.2rem 0.7rem;">
                        Remove
                      </button>
                    </form>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              <% }); %>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      <% } %>

      <p class="field-help" style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
        In your physical binder, this scene should also have its own scene-specific
        release form (SSR) where each performer signs off on the acts and partners.
        We can add SSR forms as a later step.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
